name: Ornella & FAFO
description:
With a strong foothold in Oslo’s club scene, Ornella has been an active presence behind the decks for years. She is one half of the booking team at Gehør, where she also holds a residency. A keen explorer of sound, her DJ sets are known for their eclectic range, moving fluidly through genres like house, electro, breaks, drum & bass, and techno.

FAFO (aka Lea Furaha) is an Oslo-based DJ and multidisciplinary creative. She has played her way through several venues in Oslo, and her sets have also made their way to festivals like EKKO, Jungelfest & BYLARM. 
With her fluid approach to mixing she moves freely in the electronic landscape, mixing elements from juke, house, bass, breaks and more.
